OL,3,CFamilies face struggle for places in
OL,4,CJersey's only SEND holiday club
OL,6,FThe father of a neurodiverse boy in
OL,7,FJersey says he does not know how
OL,8,Fparents will cope if the island's only
OL,9,Fholiday club for children with
OL,10,Fadditional needs cannot run more often.
OL,12,FLocal charity Centrepoint currently
OL,13,Foffers sessions across all 14 weeks of
OL,14,Fthe school holidays but only receives
OL,15,Ffunding from the Government for half
OL,16,Fof that time, which it says has left
OL,17,Fit operating at a "massive loss".
