OL,3,CFamilies face struggle for places in
OL,4,CJersey's only SEND holiday club
OL,6,FThe group's Chief Executive Officer,
OL,7,FJane Moy, told ITV News that they are
OL,8,Fonly able to offer space for 30
OL,9,Fchildren at a time, despite 98
OL,10,Ffamilies applying.
OL,12,FFor James Barrett and his son Teddy,
OL,13,Fbeing able to access the sessions is
OL,14,F"completely vital".
OL,16,FJames explains he needs certainty over
OL,17,Fwhether Centrepoint can take Teddy
OL,18,Fthroughout the holidays to help
OL,19,Fprovide his son with the sense of
OL,20,Froutine he needs to be happy and build
OL,21,Frelationships with his peers.
