OL,6,FHowever, with the limited capacity, he
OL,7,Fsometimes does not know until a few
OL,8,Fdays before the sessions take place,
OL,9,Fwhich James says causes significant
OL,10,Fstress.
OL,12,FSpeaking about the challenges he and
OL,13,Fother parents would face if their
OL,14,Fchildren could not attend the holiday
OL,15,Fclub sessions, James explained: "If
OL,16,Fthey are not worn out, they will be up
OL,17,Fall night and that then catches up
OL,18,Fwith all of us.
