OL,6,F"If it wasn't for this, I don't know
OL,7,Fhow any of the parents would cope,
OL,8,Fsurvive and be able to hold down a job
OL,9,Fbecause we don't have 25 days' holiday
OL,10,Fourselves.
OL,12,F"Not knowing in advance is the biggest
OL,13,Fstress but there are lots of parents I
OL,14,Fknow who don't always get all those
OL,15,Fdays and it's then about finding the
OL,16,Fextra days out of your own holiday."
