OL,3,CFamilies face struggle for places in
OL,4,CJersey's only SEND holiday club
OL,6,FSeeking to address concerns, Jane
OL,7,Fsaid: "We try and prioritise where we
OL,8,Fcan. We know some families don't have
OL,9,Fany support on the island, for
OL,10,Fexample, and the parents work full-
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"Even parents who don't work full-time
OL,14,Fstill need support for those children
OL,15,Fbecause as much as they love them,
OL,16,Fit's hard work looking after a child
OL,17,Fwith complex needs."
