OL,6,FHowever, Jane admitted that without
OL,7,Fmore government support, it is "really
OL,8,Fdifficult to allocate sessions fairly
OL,9,Fand equally".
OL,11,FShe added that Centrepoint had
OL,12,Fpreviously been well-supported by
OL,13,FGovernment but believes it had
OL,14,Frecently been "thrown on the
OL,15,Fbackburner".
