OL,3,CFamilies face struggle for places in
OL,4,CJersey's only SEND holiday club
OL,6,FJane wants the Government to set out
OL,7,Fexactly how many sessions they will
OL,8,Fsubsidise so the charity does not have
OL,9,Fto scramble to find enough staff at
OL,10,Fshort notice, something Jane said is
OL,11,Fan "enormous amount of pressure".
OL,13,FIn response, the Government explained
OL,14,Fthat this summer, 120 children with
OL,15,Fspecial educational needs and
OL,16,Fdisabilities (SEND) are being
OL,17,Fsupported through the short breaks
OL,18,Fholiday scheme and demand has always
OL,19,Foutstripped capacity.
